snippet.title: Paw Paw Paw Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Paw Paw Paw is a 2D side-scroller beat 'em up game developed by Simpleton. Out now on Steam and Consoles.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1037910/Paw_Paw_Paw/
Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/paw-paw-paw-switch/
PS4: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0891-CUSA24828_00-RATAGAMPAWPAWPAW
Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9p71snv0bhht

More information:
http://pawpawpawgame.com
